Package org.moeaframework.problem.CDTLZ

package org.moeaframework.problem.CDTLZ
Package for the constrained DTLZ test problems.

References:

  1. Deb, K. and H. Jain. "An Evolutionary Many-Objective Optimization Algorithm Using Reference-Point-Based Nondominated Sorting Approach, Part I: Solving Problems With Box Constraints." IEEE Transactions on Evolutionary Computation, 18(4):577-601, 2014.
  2. Jain, H. and K. Deb. "An Evolutionary Many-Objective Optimization Algorithm Using Reference-Point-Based Nondominated Sorting Approach, Part II: Handling Constraints and Extending to an Adaptive Approach." IEEE Transactions on Evolutionary Computation, 18(4):602-622, 2014.
